Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.10,0:00:36.65,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愛が愛を「重過ぎる」って理解を拒み
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.82,0:00:41.45,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,憎しみに　変わって行く前に…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.59,0:00:43.42,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,何もかもそうだろ？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.54,0:00:48.44,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,バツの悪い事情にはいつも蓋して
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.55,0:00:51.27,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,食わせ物のリアル
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.38,0:00:53.60,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歪んだジレンマ時代で
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.75,0:00:57.36,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,約束したはずの二人さえ
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.50,0:01:01.84,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,気付かず通り過ぎて行く
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.51,0:01:09.46,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,壊しあって　解り合ったことも
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.64,0:01:11.27,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,置き去りにした
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.39,0:01:14.71,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,これが成れの果てなの？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.84,0:01:19.25,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,認めないで　立ち向かったときも
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.86,0:01:25.46,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,落ちて行く時のイメージから逃げ出せずに
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.60,0:01:30.20,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Ah　何度でも探し出すよ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.30,0:01:36.95,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,君の目　その手の温もりを
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.17,0:01:42.29,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愛はいつも私を傷つけるだけ…って君はつぶやいて
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.40,0:01:46.95,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,信じる事が怖くて泣いたんだろ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.14,0:01:49.20,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弱さを知って強くなれ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.35,0:01:52.96,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恐れず信じることで
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.08,0:01:57.98,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本当の愛を知るだろう
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.10,0:00:36.65,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}{\3a&HFF}{\4a&H3F}爱太过沉重而拒绝理解
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.82,0:00:41.45,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}{\3a&HFF}{\4a&H3F}由爱生恨之前
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.59,0:00:43.42,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}{\3a&HFF}{\4a&H3F}任何事都是如此吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.54,0:00:48.44,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}{\3a&HFF}{\4a&H3F}尴尬的事由总被掩盖
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.55,0:00:51.27,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}{\3a&HFF}{\4a&H3F}这伪善者的真实
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.38,0:00:53.60,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}{\3a&HFF}{\4a&H3F}在扭曲的泥沼时代
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.75,0:00:57.36,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}{\3a&HFF}{\4a&H3F}本已约定的我们
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.50,0:01:01.84,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}{\3a&HFF}{\4a&H3F}也不觉擦肩而过
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.51,0:01:09.46,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}{\3a&HFF}{\4a&H3F}彼此伤害
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.64,0:01:11.27,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}{\3a&HFF}{\4a&H3F}抛开原有的理解
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.39,0:01:14.71,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}{\3a&HFF}{\4a&H3F}莫非这就是末路
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.84,0:01:19.25,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}{\3a&HFF}{\4a&H3F}不认同命运 奋起反抗之时
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.86,0:01:25.46,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}{\3a&HFF}{\4a&H3F}也无法逃离坠落时的幻影
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.60,0:01:30.20,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}{\3a&HFF}{\4a&H3F}Ah 多少次我都能寻到
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.30,0:01:36.95,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}{\3a&HFF}{\4a&H3F}你的瞳眸 温暖的手
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.17,0:01:40.39,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}{\3a&HFF}{\4a&H3F}「爱永远只能给我伤害」
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.49,0:01:42.29,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}{\3a&HFF}{\4a&H3F}你喃喃自语
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.40,0:01:46.95,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}{\3a&HFF}{\4a&H3F}是否曾因害怕相信而哭泣
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.14,0:01:49.20,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}{\3a&HFF}{\4a&H3F}承认脆弱 变得坚强
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.35,0:01:52.96,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}{\3a&HFF}{\4a&H3F}不再畏惧 努力相信
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.08,0:01:57.98,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}{\3a&HFF}{\4a&H3F}定能找到真爱
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.44,0:00:07.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿撒迪斯坦…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.01,0:00:08.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在燃烧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.94,0:00:12.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么阿撒迪斯坦会…为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.88,0:00:16.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这规模…不是恐怖袭击
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.21,0:00:21.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是…Gundam
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.27,0:00:24.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且那涂装…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.15,0:00:25.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道是
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.90,0:00:31.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错 你猜对了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.31,0:02:08.86,title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)}{\pos(549,108)}{\3a&HC9&\4c&H000000&\1c&HFEFDFF&}伤痕
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.01,0:02:11.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把伤兵搬到这边
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.90,0:02:14.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,改变照明角度
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.34,0:02:15.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,免得被敌人发现
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.54,0:02:24.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太 太过分了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.39,0:02:25.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了 轰隆
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.76,0:02:28.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别让孩子们过来
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.47,0:02:29.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,暂时待在掩体里
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.30,0:02:31.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…是
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.90,0:02:33.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,席琳
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.28,0:02:35.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,克劳斯
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.80,0:02:39.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,克劳斯 你没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.09,0:02:41.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还好
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.47,0:02:44.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 基地的情况你都看到了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.87,0:02:48.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,花费三年以上才建造的基地…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.80,0:02:52.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是你们泄露了这里的情报吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.39,0:02:53.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们没有
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.68,0:02:54.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都怪你们
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.94,0:02:56.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是你们害死了我们的同伴
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.87,0:02:59.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别这样 他们什么也没做
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.11,0:03:01.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁知道啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.27,0:03:02.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,相信我
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.49,0:03:04.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 我们的同伴…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.32,0:03:07.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚才还喜笑颜开的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.02,0:03:10.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道 会报仇的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.89,0:03:14.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底 是谁向A-LAWS告密的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.49,0:03:33.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你做了什么
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.45,0:03:35.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我 我…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.98,0:03:36.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是你干的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.38,0:03:38.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是谁
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.63,0:03:39.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,A-LAWS的间谍吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.86,0:03:41.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是 我只是…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.53,0:03:47.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说说理由吧 沙慈·库斯洛德
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.84,0:03:56.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这真是… 这就是他们的做法
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.91,0:03:57.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶的A-LAWS
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.42,0:03:59.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,米蕾娜别看
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.86,0:04:01.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好…好的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.10,0:04:05.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,生于战火 又魂归战火
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.64,0:04:06.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,若这就是命运
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.59,0:04:09.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,若这就是命运
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.23,0:04:11.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,必无法违抗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.81,0:04:19.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,生于战火
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.11,0:04:21.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有可能是友军
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.58,0:04:22.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又魂归战火
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.73,0:04:26.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,若这就是命运
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.28,0:04:29.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,必无法违抗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.51,0:04:30.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是敌人?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.62,0:04:32.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,踏上看不见的旅途
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.88,0:04:37.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,道路的尽头是 生命的终焉
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.12,0:04:41.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这正是 神之引导
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.81,0:04:46.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,埃米利奥
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.60,0:04:49.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,埃米利奥
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.29,0:04:53.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂…喂
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.73,0:04:54.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了 皇小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.28,0:04:55.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,皇小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.20,0:05:01.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,何等…何等愚蠢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.28,0:05:05.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我没想到 会变成这样
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.27,0:05:09.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只是想摆脱战争
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.60,0:05:12.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没想到竟然…我…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.12,0:05:15.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是你夺走了他们的生命
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.79,0:05:18.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是你愚蠢的行为
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.72,0:05:21.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自己不一样 自己和这无关
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.88,0:05:23.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是不同世界的事
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.78,0:05:25.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是你这种逃避现实的行为
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.34,0:05:27.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,化为无意识的恶意
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.99,0:05:29.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,招致这种结果
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.01,0:05:36.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…我也不想这样
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.79,0:05:40.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,提耶利亚
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.05,0:05:41.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刹那
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.18,0:05:44.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.42,0:05:45.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,A-LAWS干的好事
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.61,0:05:48.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而原因在他
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.07,0:05:53.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沙慈·库斯洛德
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.40,0:06:01.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是回阿撒迪斯坦去了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.51,0:06:02.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,席琳
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.02,0:06:06.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿撒迪斯坦被…我们的祖国…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.15,0:06:08.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿撒迪斯坦?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.45,0:06:16.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽因Gundam节外生枝损失了两机
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.81,0:06:20.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过还是成功摧毁了反联邦组织的秘密基地
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.72,0:06:23.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这可是大功一件啊 玛内金上校
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.13,0:06:24.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住口
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.03,0:06:27.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 您不喜欢扫荡作战吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.15,0:06:29.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可是喜好非常
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.35,0:06:31.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,杀人有那么开心吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.44,0:06:35.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为何如此激动
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.04,0:06:39.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您过去不也做过同样的事吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.12,0:06:43.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀呀 那可真是不幸的事故
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.23,0:06:47.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由于情报有误 变成友军相残
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.54,0:06:51.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当时您应该是AEU的战术预报员
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.54,0:06:52.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别说了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.43,0:06:55.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又想对同伴出手吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.40,0:07:00.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,经历了那种事 本应再也不愿涉足战场了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.94,0:07:02.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可您怎么还恋恋不舍呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.17,0:07:10.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我尊敬您 玛内金上校
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.71,0:07:19.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿撒迪斯坦遭到了攻击?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.09,0:07:21.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是联邦干的吗 
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.55,0:07:22.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.29,0:07:27.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但在发动攻击的MS中有Gundam
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.94,0:07:28.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Gundam?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.68,0:07:31.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那架机体恐怕是…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.61,0:07:35.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,皇小姐好像晕倒了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.40,0:07:35.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.14,0:07:36.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.33,0:07:38.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.57,0:07:40.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,托勒密发来了返航命令
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.86,0:07:42.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道了 回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.32,0:07:44.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也来
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.50,0:07:47.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,待在这里不知会遭到什么待遇
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.88,0:07:56.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都市区域的主要设施几乎都被破坏了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.29,0:08:00.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,警察 军队都瘫痪了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.45,0:08:03.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使如此 我还是对那国家…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.78,0:08:06.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想救拉撒托付给我的国家
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.90,0:08:08.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亏你能回来
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.25,0:08:12.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是刹那硬带我回来的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.89,0:08:14.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要感谢他才是了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.49,0:08:16.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢什么 我情愿死在那里
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.25,0:08:19.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,若为了阿撒迪斯坦 我情愿…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.34,0:08:24.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玛莉娜
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.90,0:08:35.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天人似乎在尽快准备离开这里的器材和食物
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.91,0:08:37.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在往其他设施搬运完毕之前
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.38,0:08:39.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们负责防卫
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.12,0:08:43.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗 请代我传达感激之情
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.11,0:08:48.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底是谁泄露了这里的情报
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.67,0:08:51.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,问我这间谍有什么用?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.98,0:08:57.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真善良啊 新生的天人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.62,0:09:00.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底是受谁影响呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.96,0:09:03.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小姐 让我来准备那件事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.76,0:09:05.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我交给妮娜·崔尼蒂了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.50,0:09:07.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.14,0:09:10.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你能使用脑量子波吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.36,0:09:11.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这…这个
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.14,0:09:16.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了瞒过变革者 她的能力是不可或缺的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.86,0:09:20.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而你不合适 红龙
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.77,0:09:22.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 兄长
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.59,0:09:31.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也和他一样吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.40,0:09:37.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由于精神受到打击 暂时性意识紊乱
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.68,0:09:40.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,过些时间就会清醒吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.73,0:09:42.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,皇小姐到底发生了什么事
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.45,0:09:48.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道 但原因一定是这次屠杀事件
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.18,0:09:51.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,埃米利奥
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.35,0:09:55.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我相信你的战术预报
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.39,0:09:58.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,根据错误的情报 你们分别进行了预报
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.01,0:10:02.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由此演变成友军相残
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.78,0:10:04.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你没有逃避战争
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.73,0:10:08.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而是为了尽快结束战争而努力 我尊敬你
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.73,0:10:10.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们太优秀了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.36,0:10:12.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玛内金
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.08,0:10:14.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的埃米利奥
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.20,0:10:14.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,九条
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.43,0:10:21.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Gundam的战术很像她的作风
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.17,0:10:23.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莫非是九条
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.70,0:10:39.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就是…不 那才是真正的战场
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.44,0:10:45.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上校的密信
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.85,0:10:49.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为何用顶武专用的暗号
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.33,0:10:54.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉用这麻烦的方式联络
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.81,0:10:57.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是为了避免被A-LAWS发现
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.97,0:11:01.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听说中尉参加了KATARON扫荡作战
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.83,0:11:05.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为此我必须向你谢罪
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.22,0:11:07.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢罪?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.21,0:11:13.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,根据上校收到的情报 才实行了那作战?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.85,0:11:14.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么会
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.49,0:11:17.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上校自己一定也很难过
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.20,0:11:20.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还如此为我担心
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.63,0:11:25.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要收我做养女?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.84,0:11:28.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然要你同意
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.67,0:11:31.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.50,0:11:35.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,索玛·史米卢佐夫这名字太拗口吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.43,0:11:36.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有的事
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.61,0:11:41.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 要舍弃比利斯这名字
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.46,0:11:42.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我觉得有些寂寥
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.87,0:11:45.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你喜欢这个名字吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.63,0:11:50.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不想忘记曾被人这样称呼过
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.21,0:11:58.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢您 上校
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.17,0:12:00.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多亏上校我才能重新认识
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.05,0:12:05.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,超人特务机关超兵1号这个身份
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.92,0:12:07.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是兵器
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.47,0:12:08.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是杀人的工具
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.44,0:12:11.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可能获得幸福…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.96,0:12:17.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真失态啊 史米卢佐夫上校
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.85,0:12:20.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然让KATARON成员逃掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.73,0:12:23.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样我们特地前来不就毫无意义了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.81,0:12:25.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上校
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.51,0:12:26.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你竟然对上官…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.97,0:12:30.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们是政府直辖的独立治安维持部队
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.83,0:12:34.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别跟联邦军的军阶混为一谈
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.64,0:12:35.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,十分抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.15,0:12:38.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这次由我负全责
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.92,0:12:42.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在上层决定处分之前 请继续执行任务
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.73,0:12:43.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.98,0:12:56.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,攻击阿撒迪斯坦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.23,0:12:59.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让联邦着手重组中东
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.98,0:13:04.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做得真绝啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.32,0:13:07.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没办法 没办法
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.66,0:13:09.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 干活干活
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,==================================
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.84,0:13:24.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,巴拉克·吉宁上尉以下五人 作为补充人员前来报到
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.04,0:13:26.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我叫卡蒂·玛内金
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.84,0:13:29.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上尉 你为何加入A-LAWS
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.50,0:13:33.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,甘愿成为统一世界的铺路石 主动志愿加入
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.97,0:13:34.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不会后悔吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.23,0:13:35.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不会
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.65,0:13:37.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.01,0:13:47.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,皇小姐的情况如何
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.67,0:13:48.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还没清醒
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.10,0:13:51.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也许还需要时间静养
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.96,0:13:53.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,KATARON方面的情况呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.80,0:13:54.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,显示在屏幕上
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.45,0:13:59.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,KATARON成员的移送工作按预定在12：00开始
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.87,0:14:04.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,A-LAWS会来 必来无疑
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.77,0:14:05.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.05,0:14:06.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出动Gundam
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.22,0:14:11.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是战术呢 皇小姐病倒的情况下…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.37,0:14:12.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那也只有硬着头皮上
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.40,0:14:17.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把托勒密开往海岸线 为了让敌人发现我们
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.88,0:14:18.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.89,0:14:20.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,普特莱玛奥斯 出发
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.15,0:14:50.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,独立治安维持部队镇压反政府势力的作战
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.62,0:14:54.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,招致了各地报复性的恐怖袭击
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.53,0:14:56.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我做的事发展成这样
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.83,0:14:59.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我该怎么办好
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.29,0:15:04.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐 路易丝
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.00,0:15:07.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,光学迷彩 解除
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.74,0:15:12.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,预计监视卫星将在00:37后捕捉到
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.11,0:15:15.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全员 第一级战斗准备
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.32,0:15:15.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.74,0:15:26.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是超兵 必须忠实执行任何任务
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.35,0:15:29.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为此而诞生的存在
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.94,0:15:33.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打扰了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.52,0:15:34.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.91,0:15:35.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,失礼
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.36,0:15:37.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.91,0:15:41.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作为补充成员到任的路易丝·阿勒威准尉
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.96,0:15:45.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,MS部队所属 索玛·比利斯中尉
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.48,0:15:50.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非常抱歉 中尉 随意就和您打招呼
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.04,0:15:52.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无妨
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.60,0:15:55.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在勉强自己
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.14,0:15:59.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的脑量子波感觉到
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.53,0:16:02.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的心在哭泣
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.85,0:16:03.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.06,0:16:06.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直想念着某人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.44,0:16:09.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,中尉 原来你在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.92,0:16:11.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作战会议的时间到了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.94,0:16:14.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.07,0:16:16.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,路易丝·阿勒威准尉
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.58,0:16:20.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少尉 回礼
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.75,0:16:23.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,安德烈·史米卢佐夫少尉
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.64,0:16:30.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是少女啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.17,0:16:35.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,监视卫星掌握了天人的位置
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.59,0:16:37.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,MS队按E-3战术计划…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.94,0:16:41.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肩载两台动力炉的Gundam由我去关照
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.00,0:16:44.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,干涉 助阵 一律不用
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.42,0:16:45.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.04,0:16:47.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有何不可 上校
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.28,0:16:53.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,久闻拥有许可证的Mr.武士道大名 早就想拜见你的实力了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.15,0:16:56.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如你所愿 告辞
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.16,0:17:02.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作战开始
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.14,0:17:06.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敌人差不多该来了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.53,0:17:07.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出动Gundam
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.73,0:17:10.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第一 第二甲板打开闸门
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.82,0:17:13.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Seravee Arios 准备出击
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.23,0:17:16.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弹射甲板电压上升
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.06,0:17:19.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,发射时机移交给Seravee
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.80,0:17:23.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白 Seravee 提耶利亚·艾迪出击
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.41,0:17:27.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算没脑量子波…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.08,0:17:31.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,控制权移交
